     H            Y/
     F** ABBR34 **************************************************************
     F*  FORECAST HISTORY INQUIRY (DISPLAY QTY=0)                            *
     F*  JW       2025.12.05                                                 *
     F* -----------------------------------------
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'ABBR34'
     F*                    PARM           P@TOKU  4
     F*                    PARM           P@NONY  4
     F*                    PARM           P@NKOJ  1
     F*                    PARM           P@NUKE  5
     F*                    PARM           P@MHIN 20
     F*                    PARM           P@RTN   1
     F*   IN  P@TOKU  4A  CUSTOMER#
     F*       P@NONY  4A  DELIVERY#
     F*       P@NKOJ  1A  FACTORY
     F*       P@NUKE  5A  DOCK (PLANT FOR FORD)
     F*       P@MHIN 20A  USER PAR#
     F*   OUT P@RTN   1A  RETURN (1: ERROR, 0: NORMAL RETURN)
     F************************************************************************
     FABBPW34 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     F                                        RRN1  KSFILE SFL01
     F                                              KINFDS @INFDS
     FABBPL51 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABFPL16 IF  E           K        DISK
     FABFPL14 IF  E           K        DISK
     F            ABFPP101                          KRENAMEABF14R
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     E                    CMD1    1   5 75
     E                    ERR     1  10 60
      *
     E                    DT1         7  8 0
     E                    DT2       100  8 0
     E                    QTY         7  7 0
     E                    XTY         7  9
      *
     E                    DTE         7  6 0
      *
     E                    D1M         9  3
     E                    DAT        50  8 0
     E                    YM          9  6 0
     E                    W9YM        9  6 0
     E                    DLV        50  9
      *------------------------------------------------------------
     I@INFDS      DS
     I                                    B 378 3790@@REC
     I            DS
